Package: creature-listener
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wake word conversational interface for Beaky
 Listens for the wake word "Beaky", records speech, transcribes it
 with whisper.cpp, streams the response from an LLM, and sends
 sentences to creature-server for TTS and animated playback.
